{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782387325147,"sessionID":"ses_101725145ffej8BoFsdX6HrgJf","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"call_SnrdvksZ8c3vlPOWq7wsZKUh","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"path":"D:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie","include":"*.md","pattern":"patch_authority.py --kind matrix|\"set\"|featureId"},"output":"Found 56 matches\nD:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\scripts\\README.zh.md:\n  Line 169: 覆盖报告用于减少功能覆盖差距和无法解释的代码规模差距：它会列出关键源文件、源功能覆盖矩阵、验证结果、阶段任务清单内嵌行为审计、平台能力检查、资源/本地化覆盖、目标侧 placeholder/stub/in-memory/deferred 等弱化信号，以及 target/source 规模比例。`plan-seed.*` 会把 Java/Kotlin/ArkTS 或 mixed Android 静态分析压缩成统一的 source units、callable/UI/data/resource/platform contracts、phase/group candidates 和 analysis gaps，作为 planning 的跨语言索引；planning 后的 `plan-validation-report.*` 会检查 strict JSON、canonical phase、implementation group ownership 和 authority plannedPhase 对齐。`source-coverage-matrix-template.*` 和 `platform-capability-template.*` 每次按源项目重新生成；`source-coverage-matrix.json/md` 与 `platform-capability-check.json/md` 是 agent 维护的工作记录。`verification-results.*` 会自动汇总 build gate 产物，并保留后续可手工/脚本写入的测试或模拟器验证结果；Cangjie test build gate 会写入 `test-build-reports/<phase>/test-build-report.*`，macOS、Windows、Linux 的运行说明见 [`scripts/docs/cangjie-test-gate.md`](docs/cangjie-test-gate.md)。可选 runtime UI smoke 可以通过 `shared/reports/runtime_ui_smoke.py` 生成，会写入 `runtime-ui-reports/<phase>/runtime-ui-report.*`，记录可选 HAP 指纹、`hdc list targets`、显式启动命令和可选布局 dump；默认只记录 `BLOCKED/SKIPPED/PASS/FAIL` 证据，不因没有设备或没有启动配置中断正常翻译流程，只有加 `--fail-on-runtime-failure` 时才把 runtime smoke 变成硬门禁。`phase-task-checklist.*` 内嵌的 `behaviorAudit` 是从矩阵、平台能力和验证结果派生出来的当前阶段审计视图，不是新的状态源。`source-coverage-matrix-template.*` 的 `featureId` 会把完整源路径、功能序号、功能名和 feature point 算入短 hash，避免长路径只因可读前缀截断而撞 id。`source-coverage-matrix.json` 缺失时会从模板初始化；已存在时，如果它来自旧 `featureIdVersion`，脚本会直接按当前模板重建，不迁移旧 id；同一 id 版本内才会用当前模板同步 active entries，并按 `featureId`，或在生成 id 漂移时按 `sourcePath + featurePoint/featureName` 继承 agent 已维护的 status、phase、`sourceBehavior`、`targetBehavior`、`verificationEvidence`、`parityLevel`、target endpoints、tests、notes 和 deferred 字段。不再匹配当前模板的旧条目会保留在 `staleEntries`，不参与 coverage gate；模板或矩阵出现重复 `featureId` 会作为结构问题报告，不会静默 sync。这样可以避免源码 checkout 或扫描器变化导致大量 `coverage-matrix-missing-entry` 账本错误，同时把新发现的功能如实暴露为 planned/uncovered 工作量。\n\n\nD:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\scripts\\README.md:\n  Line 223: from the current source scan. Template `featureId` values include a short hash\n\n  Line 227: matrix was produced with an older `featureIdVersion`, the workflow rebuilds it\n\n  Line 231: endpoint, test, note, and deferred fields are carried forward by `featureId`,\n\n  Line 235: matrix duplicate `featureId` values are reported as structural problems instead\n\n\nD:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\docs\\unified-cangjie-translation-workflow.zh.md:\n  Line 84: `source-coverage-matrix.json` 和 `platform-capability-check.json` 虽然仍是 agent 维护的权威文件，但大批量或关键字段更新应优先通过 `scripts/shared/source_coverage/patch_authority.py` 执行。该工具读取严格 JSON patch payload，通过 `featureId` / `capabilityId` 定位行，支持 `set`、`append`、`remove` 和少量新增行，并在写回前校验字段白名单、status/parity 一致性、critical/high 必填证据、deferred blocker/fallback/future path，以及 active entries 的重复 id。工具写回 JSON 后会直接同步对应 Markdown mirror，避免 agent 临时拼超长 shell 或整文件重写时造成 JSON 失败、字段漂移、Markdown 与 authority 不一致。\n\n\nD:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\docs\\arkts-to-cangjie-agent-protocol.md:\n  Line 102: Use `plan-seed` as the compact cross-language planning index when present. Map its source units, callable method/event-handler contracts, UI contracts, data contracts, resource contracts, platform capability contracts, structure risks, and analysis gaps into `plan.json` phases and implementation groups. Each group should include stable `groupId`, `title`, `groupType`, `priority`, `sourcePaths`, callable contract references when available, `featureIds`, `resourceInputs`, `platformCapabilityIds`, UI/data contract references or hints, `expectedTargetDomains`, `requiredBehaviors`, `riskHints`, and `acceptanceEvidence`. Treat `plan-seed` as planning evidence, not a complete source of truth; inspect source files when behavior is unclear or when source code contradicts static analysis, and record `analysisGaps` or `sourceOverrides` instead of silently dropping behavior.\n\n\nD:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\Kotlin2Cangjie\\docs\\android-kotlin-to-cangjie-agent-protocol.md:\n  Line 106: Each implementation group in `plan.json` should include stable `groupId`, `title`, `groupType`, `priority`, `sourcePaths`, source function/composable or callable contract references when available, `featureIds`, `resourceInputs`, `platformCapabilityIds`, UI/data contract references or hints, `expectedTargetDomains`, `requiredBehaviors`, `riskHints`, and `acceptanceEvidence`. Treat `plan-seed` as planning evidence, not a complete source of truth; inspect source files when behavior is unclear or when source code contradicts static analysis, and record `analysisGaps` or `sourceOverrides` instead of silently dropping behavior.\n\n\nD:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\docs\\android-java-to-cangjie-agent-protocol.md:\n  Line 99: Each implementation group in `plan.json` should include stable `groupId`, `title`, `groupType`, `priority`, `sourcePaths`, source method or callable contract references when available, `featureIds`, `resourceInputs`, `platformCapabilityIds`, UI/data contract references or hints, `expectedTargetDomains`, `requiredBehaviors`, `riskHints`, and `acceptanceEvidence`. Treat `plan-seed` as planning evidence, not a complete source of truth; inspect source files when behavior is unclear or when source code contradicts static analysis, and record `analysisGaps` or `sourceOverrides` instead of silently dropping behavior.\n\n\nD:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\src\\cangjie-skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\lang-features\\class_and_interface\\prop\\属性\\属性_261f428b.md:\n  Line 23:             println(\"set\")\r\n\n\nD:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\src\\cangjie-skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\ark